DISK (Physical Reality)
-----------------------
Block 900   ← data
Block 901   ← data
Block 1200  ← data
⚙️ Who does this?
👉 Filesystem (like ext4) using:

inode

extent tree (modern systems)

metadata structures

⚡ Why This Exists
Because:

Files are not stored contiguously

Disk gets fragmented over time

Filesystem needs flexibility

